Follow not the Paſtors of this Land, for the Sun is gone down upon them;
as the Lord liveth, they lead you from Chriſt and the good old way.
Sam. Rutherford, Epiſt. 2. To his Pariſhioners.

Mr. Matthew Selkirk preaching againſt keeping of days, ſaid, They that
keep † Yule-day,Chriſtmaſs. Sirs, deny that Chriſt came in the fleſh, and are rank Jews;
& they keep that day in commemoration of J. Caeſar the chief of the Jews.
